    {
      "locale": "ruRU",
      "text": "\"Это все шествие? Я дума{mf|л|ла} их будет больше\".",
      "modification_date": "2026-03-25T13:17:36.4740544Z",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "CheckMe",
          "trait_date": "2025-11-19T10:34:37.7327407Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Вигдис, откуда на мостике эти люди?\"",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "enGB",
      "text": "\"Is this the entire procession? I thought there would be more of them.\"",
